399
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:36,040
Spilled glass.

400
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:36,960
It was accidentally spilled.

401
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:37,780
(Quick save attempt)

402
00:11:38,580 --> 00:11:40,660
(Straining to think)

403
00:11:40,660 --> 00:11:42,340
(Is this explanation even going to work?)
It accidentally spilled.

404
00:11:42,340 --> 00:11:43,530
It accidentally spilled.

405
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:45,440
Nice.

406
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:47,680
Liu Yuning, that's actually brilliant.

407
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:51,120
So fun.

408
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:51,680
I want to say

