Yeah.

475
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:37,280
Those walls.

476
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:39,080
The walls closed in.

477
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:39,520
Yeah.

478
00:13:40,920 --> 00:13:42,360
