We can.

480
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,100
Just act cute and whine a little.

481
00:13:46,100 --> 00:13:46,430
How?

482
00:13:46,430 --> 00:13:47,020
Beg me.

483
00:13:47,020 --> 00:13:48,250
Please, Ding.

484
00:13:48,340 --> 00:13:49,640
