523
00:15:05,030 --> 00:15:05,570
Hold on!

524
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:06,200
Beef jerky.

525
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:06,740
My strawberry!

526
00:15:07,180 --> 00:15:08,430
(Worried about the strawberry +1)
My strawberry got smashed!

527
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:10,300
