We didn't have time to react.

534
00:15:16,060 --> 00:15:17,560
Let's push it!

535
00:15:17,870 --> 00:15:19,380
(Pushing hard)
Push harder!

536
00:15:19,380 --> 00:15:21,980
(Pushing hard)

537
00:15:24,640 --> 00:15:26,580
