1954
00:55:02,120 --> 00:55:03,200
Who's the glutton?

1955
00:55:03,200 --> 00:55:03,960
We don't need to discuss

1956
00:55:03,960 --> 00:55:05,400
because he spoke later.

1957
00:55:05,400 --> 00:55:07,080
I don't understand your plan.

1958
00:55:07,080 --> 00:55:08,000
We won't lose.

1959
00:55:08,000 --> 00:55:09,120
We'll win anyway.

1960
00:55:09,120 --> 00:55:09,880
Spot on.

1961
00:55:11,740 --> 00:55:12,420
(The five overlords have assembled.
A new journey begins)

1962
00:55:12,440 --> 00:55:14,000
Which five bugs did we fix?

1963
00:55:14,000 --> 00:55:17,320
Glutton, fear of the dark,
love of dancing, playful, and dramatic.

1964
00:55:18,360 --> 00:55:19,760
Oh no. We didn't fix it.

1965
00:55:19,760 --> 00:55:20,520
Scary.

1966
00:55:20,520 --> 00:55:21,720
What?

1967
00:56:09,650 --> 00:56:13,650
♪Come now, players all,
let the game of reason start♪

1968
00:56:13,650 --> 00:56:18,090
♪Unlock each hidden trial,
let courage spark the dark♪

1969
00:56:20,110 --> 00:56:24,270
♪Night falls slow, shadows grow,
the sleuth is lost inside the maze♪

1970
00:56:24,270 --> 00:56:28,490
♪Figures pass, lanterns sparse,
dark currents drift without a trace♪

1971
00:56:28,490 --> 00:56:32,260
♪Wind picks up, footsteps rush,
cold laughter swallowed by the dark♪

1972
00:56:32,260 --> 00:56:36,370
♪Truth concealed, the night
stands still, and nothing leaves a mark♪

1973
00:56:36,550 --> 00:56:40,670
♪An unsigned letter, coded words,
the solvers gather one by one♪

1974
00:56:40,670 --> 00:56:44,780
♪A broken game, illusion reigns,
who's hiding what they've done?♪

1975
00:56:44,780 --> 00:56:48,420
♪Hushed voices, nerves on edge,
wrapped in smoke and mirrors still♪

1976
00:56:48,420 --> 00:56:50,550
♪The next second, deeper riddles,
or the answer to the kill♪

1977
00:56:50,550 --> 00:56:54,500
♪Every piece of truth
has finally come to light♪

1978
00:56:54,740 --> 00:56:58,660
♪Unlock the mystery, turn the question,
let's begin tonight♪

1979
00:56:58,870 --> 00:57:03,020
♪Side by side, no holding back,
follow every clue to find the truth♪

1980
00:57:03,020 --> 00:57:06,580
♪The story blurs like flowers in fog,
let's begin tonight♪

1981
00:57:06,840 --> 00:57:11,490
♪Search for the vanished cipher,
trace the proof, and face the sleuth♪
